        <updateDate>2009-02-26T16:47:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Highway Trust Fund Reform Act of 2009 - Repeals the Davis-Bacon Act (which requires that the locally prevailing wage rate be paid to laborers and mechanics working on federal-aid highway construction projects and public transportation construction projects).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
